Document: RefCounted
Path: godot/classes/class_refcounted.rst
Summary: Base class for reference-counted objects in Godot.

RefCounted is the base class for objects that manage their own memory using reference counting. This means that instead of manually freeing memory, the object keeps track of how many references point to it. When the reference count drops to zero, the object is automatically freed. This is a common pattern in many programming languages and game engines to prevent memory leaks and simplify memory management.

Inherits: Object

