Document: RefCounted
Path: godot/classes/class_refcounted.rst
Summary: Provides methods for managing reference counts in Godot objects.

Method: get_reference_count() -> int
Returns the current reference count.

Method: init_ref() -> bool
Initializes the internal reference counter. Use this only if you really know what you are doing.
Returns whether the initialization was successful.

Method: reference() -> bool
Increments the internal reference counter. Use this only if you really know what you are doing.
Returns true if the increment was successful, false otherwise.

Method: unreference() -> bool
Decrements the internal reference counter. Use this only if you really know what you are doing.
Returns true if the object should be freed after the decrement, false otherwise.